-- Yemeni Soldier Dies After Blast at Weapons Depot, Official Says
-- B y   M o h a m m e d   H a t e m
-- 2012-10-18T12:28:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-10-18/yemeni-soldier-dies-after-blast-at-weapons-depot-official-says.html
An explosion at a weapons depot in
the Yemeni capital today killed one soldier and wounded two
others, an official said.  The blast occurred after the tire of a vehicle caught fire
during military training, Abdulghani al-Shameri, an aide to the
commander of the First Armored Division, Major General Ali
Mohssein al-Ahmer, said in a phone interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
